com.foreach.across.modules.web.resource

Interface WebResourceRule

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AddPackageResourceRule, AddWebResourceRule, RemoveWebResourceRule
    Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public interface WebResourceRule

    An abstract class that can be used to single add(com.foreach.across.modules.web.ui.ViewElementBuilder) a CssWebResourceBuilder, JavascriptWebResourceBuilder or ViewElementBuilderSupport.

    A WebResourcePackage can be added with addPackage(String)

    Since:
    3.2.0
    Author:
    Marc Vanbrabant
